Package util

package util
  • Classes
    Class
    Description
    CircularLinkedList
    Represents a circular linked list that stores Technician objects.
    Date
    Represents a date with year, month, and day, and includes methods for validating the date, checking for leap years, and comparing dates.
    List<E>
    A generic dynamic array implementation of a list that allows for adding, removing, and accessing elements, along with iterator functionality.

    A class representing a node in a linked list that holds a Technician object.
